My first mini project using the &lt;a href="http://www.mapeditor.org/">Tiled&lt;/a> application was an enjoyable experience.  A friend of mine made a multiplayer PvP top down shooter game with a html 5 platform.  He had several placeholder graphics that I was able to re-skin to give the game it&amp;rsquo;s own unique flavor.  See the original screen capture below for comparison.
